data.description: From behind the brick facade, 15239 Brazil Cir invites you into the 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhouse in Woodbridge VA.  Come in through the entry way and make your way up the first set of stairs where you’ll emerge into the primary living area. Plush carpet and natural light fill the living room which effortlessly flows into the kitchen. In the kitchen, the backsplash adds a dash of elegance against the white cabinets, while the select stainless steel appliances – including a fridge, stove, and dishwasher serve as accents as you look onto the attached breakfast nook. The sliding glass door will lead you from the breakfast nook to the private deck, great for entertaining and letting in natural light. Up the second set of stairs, the  top floor is home to all of the 3 bedrooms with the primary bathroom sporting a full ensuite bathroom.  Diving into the basement, the 1900+sqft townhouse shows off its final living area where you’re more than welcomed to get cozy by the fireplace for a night in! Home was just freshly painted! Welcome to the next chapter of your story.
